        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Flag Code Modernization Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill revises provisions regarding customs and practices with respect to the American flag.</p> <p>Among other changes, the bill permits U.S. postal workers to wear the flag on their uniforms and modifies provisions regarding the position and manner of display of the flag.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
